A little tuto to learn how to get free ai api key with OpenRouter. Start by creating an OpenRouter account at https://www.openrouter.ai/ (or login if you have already created one). Once you do it, navigate to the API section on the dashboard. Click on create key button. This will generate your api key. Save it in a secure location, you won't able to see it again ! You will need it when you use a model. After, you will have to paste your api key when you will add a model.
